column2: SELECT visit.*, star.nvisits, star.vhelio_avg, star.vscatter, aspcap.teff, aspcap.teff_err, aspcap.logg, aspcap.logg_err, aspcap.params.m_h, aspcap.params.m_h_err, aspcap.fe_h, aspcap.fe_h_err into mydb.allinfo_visits_dr1# from apogeeVisit visit JOIN apogeeStarVisit starvisit on visit.visit_id = starvisit.visit_id JOIN aspcapStar aspcap on aspcap.apstar_id = starvisit.apstar_id JOIN apogeeStar star on star.apstar_id = starvisit.apstar_id WHERE (aspcap.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag (#) ) = # and aspcap.teff > # and (star.starflag & dbo.fApogeeStarFlag (#) ) = # and star.nvisits > # ORDER BY visit.apogee_id
